        "id": 1079748
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-04-18T23:05:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "How is this any more dangerous that stashing away shared_ptrs in callbacks that get called on the event loop / ParallelTask?\n\nIn this case, locking our object across \"the remaining files to push\" turned out to be cleaner than stashing it into a ParallelTask that is pushing just the current file. I had actually done something similar to ScreenCapturer earlier, but that turned out to be more complex.",
      "parentUuid": "4881acc7_93dd73ff",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 115,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 115,
        "endChar": 17
      },
      "revId": "2c24484b46f7893c6af666d2c6ffeff6606e0b5a",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "08fc147c_f28360f5",
